sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / UI BFF
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant MR as model-registry (proxy)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL 3306 / PostgreSQL 5432<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as inferenceservice-controller<br/>8081/TCP
    participant CSI as mr-storage-initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant S3 as S3/HTTP/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AsyncJob as async-upload Job<br/>Python
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sigstore as Sigstore Services<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API

    Client->>Istio: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Istio mTLS
    Istio->>MR: Forward (mTLS ISTIO_MUTUAL)<br/>AuthorizationPolicy
    MR->>DB: INSERT (MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol)<br/>Username/Password from Secret
    DB-->>MR: Result
    MR-->>Istio: 201 Created (JSON)
    Istio-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI, MR: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync (Controller)

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService CRs<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    Controller->>MR: PUT /inference_services<br/>HTTP / Bearer Token
    MR->>DB: UPSERT serving state
    DB-->>MR: Result
    MR-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch ISVC labels<br/>HTTPS / SA Token

    Note over CSI, S3: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer

    Note right of CSI: KServe invokes as init container
    CSI->>MR: GET /model_versions/{id}/artifacts<br/>HTTP / No auth
    MR-->>CSI: Artifact URI (s3://... or https://...)
    CSI->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS / Storage credentials
    S3-->>CSI: Model files

    Note over AsyncJob, Sigstore: Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job

    AsyncJob->>S3: GET source model artifacts<br/>HTTPS / AWS IAM
    S3-->>AsyncJob: Model files
    AsyncJob->>OCI: Push model image<br/>HTTPS / Registry credentials
    OCI-->>AsyncJob: Image digest
    AsyncJob->>Sigstore: Sign model (Fulcio/Rekor/TSA)<br/>HTTPS / K8s SA Token (OIDC)
    Sigstore-->>AsyncJob: Signature + transparency entry
    AsyncJob->>MR: POST /model_artifacts<br/>HTTP / Bearer Token
    MR->>DB: INSERT artifact record
    DB-->>MR: Result
    MR-->>AsyncJob: 201 Created
